      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Pinterest – Workflow 1: Prepare Pins (runs weekly)\n\n**What it does:** finds newly Posted blogs, reads the blog page, pulls all content images, plans pins (1 carousel of 3 hero images + single pins for the rest, 3/month), AI writes title/description/alt, auto-assigns Board from the Tailwind Boards tab by Category (AI picks the best fit when a category has more than one board), auto-sets Approval = Approved, and writes review rows to the Pinterest Pins tab -- no manual board pick or approval step.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Credentials: Google Sheets OAuth2 + OpenAI API key on the relevant nodes.\n2. Make sure the Tailwind Boards tab has a Category column filled in for the categories you want auto-assigned (a board's Category cell can list more than one, e.g. `Bathtub | Fireplace`).\n3. Add Pinterest Status column to Blogs.\n4. Check Set Config values.\n\n**Note:** the image-extraction selector (Extract & Plan) may need tuning to your live blog HTML.",
